  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t炮火连天枪弹四射的战场上，命在旦夕之间，<b>居然还要兵丁携带生米做食粮！还要煮！还要生火！？</b>猪啊猪🐷，难怪近日猪匪的伪“潜艇”仅仅由于生火做饭便爆炸沉没！土匪中共的愚蠢，超出人类的想象。就这还妄想 “超越” 美国呢！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS85V1N3bW5LLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/9WSwmnK.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9WSwmnK.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9WSwmnK.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9xdHhvcEJtLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/qtxopBm.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qtxopBm.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qtxopBm.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n参看：<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67331\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67331\">长津湖战役中中共 “空军” 无影无踪的丑态原因</a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67328\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67328\">朝鲜战争，中国参战是完全的错</a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67233\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67233\">1950年底美军及共匪双方在长津湖地区参战及伤亡人数</a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67120\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67120\">1950年平安夜，韩国长津湖中共匪军被美军狠揍的血腥惨象</a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67147\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/67147\">共匪无耻渲染把死伤无数完全失败的韩战长津湖战役硬吹成胜利</a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/64904\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/64904\">中共与北韩 共同作恶凶残至极不属人类</a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/64841\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/64841\">不善良 血腥嗜杀 中国共产党野兽与其它野兽豢养奴才走狗的共同特征</a> </div>",
